OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777468272
OL,3,CLorry load of roofing material fly-
OL,4,Ctipped on country road
OL,6,FA lorry load of roofing material has
OL,7,Fbeen fly-tipped on a country road in a
OL,8,FBerkshire village.
OL,10,FThe rubbish was dumped across the
OL,11,Fjunction of Stubbs Hill and Ryehurst
OL,12,FLane in Binfield overnight on Thursday
OL,13,F23 April.
OL,15,FThe waste includes roofing tiles,
OL,16,Fwooden battening, union jack bunting
OL,17,Fflags, pots and plants, and a yellow
OL,18,Fsaddle cover for a bike.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
