CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777468272
OL,3,CLorry load of roofing material fly-
OL,4,Ctipped on country road
OL,6,FThe Public Protection Partnership
OL,7,F(PPP), which works on behalf of
OL,8,FBracknell Forest Council and West
OL,9,FBerkshire Council, is appealing for
OL,10,Fanyone who may have information or
OL,11,Fdashcam footage.
OL,13,FThe PPP said: "Fly-tipping is not a
OL,14,Fvictimless crime. Every incident
OL,15,Fleaves a financial and environmental
OL,16,Fburden on the wider community, harming
OL,17,Flocal residents, landowners and the
OL,18,Fpublic purse.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777468272
OL,3,CLorry load of roofing material fly-
OL,4,Ctipped on country road
OL,6,F"Not only does the illegal dumping of
OL,7,Fwaste blight neighbourhoods and
OL,8,Fcountryside, it poses risks to
OL,9,Fwildlife, pollutes land and waterways,
OL,10,Fand creates hazards for anyone living
OL,11,For working nearby.
OL,13,F"Taxpayers ultimately shoulder the
OL,14,Fcost of clearing illegally dumped
OL,15,Fwaste, while private landowners may
OL,16,Fface substantial cleanup expenses
OL,17,Fthrough no fault of their own.
OL,19,F"Flytipping also diverts vital council
OL,20,Fresources away from essential services.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
