PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777468272
OL,3,CLorry load of roofing material fly-
OL,4,Ctipped on country road
OL,6,F"By treating our shared environment
OL,7,Fwith respect and disposing of waste
OL,8,Fresponsibly, we help maintain cleaner,
OL,9,Fsafer and healthier places for
OL,10,Feveryone.
OL,12,F"We urge everyone to dispose of waste
OL,13,Fresponsibly and report fly-tipping to
OL,14,Fhelp keep our area clean and safe.
OL,15,FThose found guilty of fly-tipping can
OL,16,Fface fines and/or a prison sentence."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
